    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "therapists and doctors and all that... i've tried. it's just a bandaid. it doesn't actually change who i am or how my life goes. it's like i'm a broken record and no matter how many times someone tries to fix the needle, it just skips back to the same spot. i'm just so done with trying to fix something that's fundamentally broken. it feels like the loop only ends one way.",
